comments: Gill (WAS) briefly engages with Anunoby (TOR) off ball.
Trent Jr. (TOR) lifts his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
Bertans (WAS) stops short in Trent Jr.'s (TOR) path and marginal contact occurs.
Siakam (TOR) does not cause the ball to take an unnatural bounce when he makes contact with the backboard.
Siakam (TOR) moves alongside of Westbrook's (WAS) path to the basket and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Bembry (TOR) cleanly blocks Gill (WAS) during his shot attempt near the rim.
Bembry (TOR) makes marginal contact with Bertans (WAS) as he brushes his head and does not affect his ability to retain possession.
Westbrook (WAS) extends his leg to the side and marginal contact occurs with Flynn (TOR), who contests the jump shot attempt.
Gill (WAS) has his foot inside of the restricted area when the contact occurs with Siakam (TOR) during his driving shot attempt.
Flynn (TOR) makes marginal contact with Neto's (WAS) arm at the start of his drive and does not affect his SQBR.
Anunoby (TOR) makes contact with the net as he contests Neto's (WAS) driving shot attempt but it does not cause the ball to take an unnatural bounce.
Trent Jr. (TOR) places his off-arm against Neto (WAS) and releases from contact as he changes directions.  Trent Jr. does not dislodge Neto from his defensive position..
